│ 1926 /// A pure virtual base class for all recipes modeling header phis,    │
│ including                                                                   │
│ 1927 /// phis for first order recurrences, pointer inductions and           │
│ reductions. The                                                             │
│ 1928 /// start value is the first operand of the recipe and the incoming    │
│ value from                                                                  │
│ 1929 /// the backedge is the second operand.                                │
│ 1930 ///                                                                    │
│ 1931 /// Inductions are modeled using the following sub-classes:            │
│ 1932 ///  * VPCanonicalIVPHIRecipe: Canonical scalar induction of the       │
│ vector loop,                                                                │
│ 1933 ///    starting at a specified value (zero for the main vector loop,   │
│ the resume                                                                  │
│ 1934 ///    value for the epilogue vector loop) and stepping by 1. The      │
│ induction                                                                   │
│ 1935 ///    controls exiting of the vector loop by comparing against the    │
│ vector trip                                                                 │
│ 1936 ///    count. Produces a single scalar PHI for the induction value per │
│ 1937 ///    iteration.                                                      │
│ 1938 ///  * VPWidenIntOrFpInductionRecipe: Generates vector values for      │
│ integer and                                                                 │
│ 1939 ///    floating point inductions with arbitrary start and step values. │
│ Produces                                                                    │
│ 1940 ///    a vector PHI per-part.                                          │
│ 1941 ///  * VPDerivedIVRecipe: Converts the canonical IV value to the       │
│ corresponding                                                               │
│ 1942 ///    value of an IV with different start and step values. Produces a │
│ single                                                                      │
│ 1943 ///    scalar value per iteration                                      │
│ 1944 ///  * VPScalarIVStepsRecipe: Generates scalar values per-lane based   │
│ on a                                                                        │
│ 1945 ///    canonical or derived induction.                                 │
│ 1946 ///  * VPWidenPointerInductionRecipe: Generate vector and scalar       │
│ values for a                                                                │
│ 1947 ///    pointer induction. Produces either a vector PHI per-part or     │
│ scalar values                                                               │
│ 1948 ///    per-lane based on the canonical induction.                      │
